item.description:
Hi Everyone! Looking forward to our next meetup. I need to change this meetup from Tuesday 6/2 to Wednesday 6/3. Sorry for any inconvenience.

Join us to share what you have manifested/attracted since the last meetup. If you're just learning to live in conscious creation, bring your questions.

We meet from 9:30-11:00. If the weather is warm and sunny, let's sit outside. Otherwise, see you at our regular table in the back!

See you there!!!

Julie
item.how_to_find_us: small private room just beyond the soda station, table in back
